CEDRIC et Eva

HOBOcedeva$Heure4 <- as.POSIXct(HOBOcedeva$Heure, format = "%H:%M:%S")
HOBOair$Heure4 <- as.POSIXct(HOBOair$Heure, format = "%H:%M:%S")

library(ggplot2)
library(scales)

plotcedeva <- ggplot() +
  geom_line(data = HOBOcedeva, aes(x = Heure4, y = `Température (°C)`), color = "blue") +
  geom_line(data = HOBOair, aes(x = Heure4, y = `Température (°C)`), color = "red") +
  labs(title = "Température de l'air et de l'eau sur le Kayak de Cédric et Eva",
       x = "Heure",
       y = "Température (°C)") +
  scale_x_datetime(date_labels = "%H:%M", date_breaks = "5 min") +
  scale_y_continuous(limits = c(7, 15),breaks = seq(7, 15, by = 0.5)) +
  annotate("text", x = as.POSIXct("11:38:00", format = "%H:%M:%S"), y = 9.0, 
           label = "Eau", color = "blue", hjust = -0.1, size=6) +
  annotate("text", x = as.POSIXct("11:38:00", format = "%H:%M:%S"), y = 12.5,
           label = "Air", color = "red", hjust = -0.1, size=6) +
  annotate("text", x = as.POSIXct("11:11:00", format = "%H:%M:%S"), y = 7,
           label = "Sortie de l'eau", angle = 90, size=6, color = "black", hjust = -0.1) +
  annotate("rect", xmin = as.POSIXct("11:07:00", format = "%H:%M:%S"), 
           xmax = as.POSIXct("11:14:00", format = "%H:%M:%S"), ymin = 7, ymax = 15,
           fill = "darkgreen", alpha = 0.2, color = "black") +
  annotate("text", x = as.POSIXct("10:30:00", format = "%H:%M:%S"), y = 14.7,
           label = "A", color = "black", hjust = -0.1, size=6)
